401
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:42,800
all cost money.

402
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:43,720
No money is left every month

403
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,920
in the salary card.

404
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:46,680
Miao is a sophomore now.

405
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:48,320
