409
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:56,280
The teacher suggested her
to have cram classes.

410
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:58,200
Yes. Cram classes are costly,

411
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,760
but we must spend money on them.

412
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:01,520
