413
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:03,480
I didn’t know it until I went to pay.

414
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,280
Where is the money?

415
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:07,600
She’s just a sophomore.

416
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:09,280
Why bother to have cram classes?

417
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,800
She’s already pressured.

418
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:12,320
That won’t help.

419
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:13,560
Don’t make a fuss.

420
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:15,440
You always follow suit.

421
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,680
Jiang is already a senior.

422
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,320
Has he ever had cram classes?

423
00:17:17,320 --> 00:17:18,680
If she was half as good as him,

424
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,720
I wouldn’t be so worried!

425
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:21,080
Don’t say these useless things.

426
00:17:21,080 --> 00:17:21,800
Where is the money?

427
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:22,600
You won.

428
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:23,520
I won’t talk.

429
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:24,680
You keep silent again.

430
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,320
Why are you silent?

431
00:17:26,320 --> 00:17:27,720
Tell me.

432
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,920
If I talk,

433
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,200
