501
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:52,200
Yes, you are.

502
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,160
I promised my dad

503
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:56,280
to get in top 200 in this monthly exam.

504
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:57,520
What?

505
00:19:57,520 --> 00:19:58,960
Top 200?

506
00:19:58,960 --> 00:19:59,800
Do you know your place

507
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,000
