There are many empty seats.

528
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,120
Yes, there are many.

529
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,840
I mean you can take another seat.

530
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,440
What on earth are you doing here?

531
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,800
I really come to study.

532
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:56,000
The modulus of a complex number
may not be a positive real number.

533
