537
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,880
Yes, this monthly exam
is very important to me.

538
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:07,720
I made a deal with my dad.

539
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:10,100
If I get into top 200 in liberal arts,

540
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:11,480
